This paper discusses the development of 6G mobile communication system, which involves network infrastructure, information theory, multimedia, artificial intelligence, and system control. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
